# TEC-VQA: dataset & runtime artefacts (distributed separately, not tracked).
# The data/ directory itself is kept via .gitkeep, and the QA annotations
# (`all_qa_data.jsonl`, ~2.8 MB) ship with the repo as the benchmark sample.
data/*
!data/.gitkeep
!data/all_qa_data.jsonl
